{
  "stem": "812.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 123,
      "text": "We spent some of our free time [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] killing the gnats, the-- the little eggs between our nails, and it would make a clicking sound.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 124,
      "text": "This was part of our-- the children's pastime, and that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 125,
      "text": "And they were the-- the eggs were particularly [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] plentiful in-- in the seams of clothing.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 126,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Toilets and washing facilities were blocks away in the most primitive outhouses.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 127,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Toilets were in the long benches with holes next to one another.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 128,
      "text": "There was no such thing as toilet paper.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 129,
      "text": "We had no toothpaste.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 130,
      "text": "We had no toothbrushes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 131,
      "text": "There was no soap.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 132,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 133,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Near the latrines, near those outhouses, near the toilets, was long pipes with trickles of-- trickles of water coming out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 134,
      "text": "That's how we had to wash ourselves.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 135,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] Life was getting increasingly more difficult.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 136,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and the filth and the-- the constant death surrounding us was just overwhelming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 137,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It was teenagers and men who were the first to die.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 138,
      "text": "And it was women, and mothers in particular, who survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 139,
      "text": "And mothers lived-- they had to live to save and to take care of their children and make sure that they would pull through.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 140,
      "text": "And it was the inner strength of my mother that really saw us through.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 141,
      "text": "She is a remarkable lady who has enormous inner strength.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 142,
      "text": "And there is no doubt in my mind that it is her strong will that saw us through.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 143,
      "text": "My mother worked in a kitchen, and my father worked in a shoe factory, where she-- where he pulled shoes apart and boots apart.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
